<paragraph id="498B3A466D0536B8586176125950A2A1" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">Type species:</paragraph>
<paragraph id="D23FCAA4FE39E2C1A94BC05A2673AB96" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">
<taxonomicName id="66D1406F46785C751092E55A42463819" authority="Fabricius, 1798" authorityName="Fabricius" authorityYear="1798" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Mulio" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Mulio bidens" order="Diptera" pageId="55" pageNumber="56" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bidens">Mulio bidens</taxonomicName>
Fabricius, 1805. Type locality: &quot;America Meridionalo&quot;.
